{"tid":2338371,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你係明恩樓居民 要點樣避強制檢測","createTime":"2020-12-24T03:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T16:44:23.000Z","uid":300420,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"372910ec0aae9392d6b22b4e989786972e4549b8","tid":2338371,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"依家成班喺地下捉人<br />\n淨係出入先要強制檢則證明<br />\n如果行樓梯/撘𨋢落低層（一樓/二樓）再揾一户跳窗出去有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇更加安全嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲早輪到我住緊嗰度 諗定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633c820455264505ae8f71094f869368506193f6","tid":2338371,"uid":367101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"On9仔黑警實守住"},{"pid":"20597ee1e8f2221a7d3b740b5fd7e6d06cfb08e7","tid":2338371,"uid":43280,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"7x24唔出街"},{"pid":"7fe5cb639f64db0ea7a55327794cc105c24c0a4d","tid":2338371,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"死咗咪唔洗檢測"},{"pid":"0d0006a58b502bc8b2b694d4ea4d7b6ed4ea9e3d","tid":2338371,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633c820455264505ae8f71094f869368506193f6","tid":2338371,"uid":367101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"On9仔黑警實守住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"所以諗緊有冇其他方法<br />\n或者可以試吓借人地份證明掃描+PS再印份假嘅出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未見過份證明 唔知有冇防偽特徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55d6427a93a7ab01ae0977332e7cfbe64166f42","tid":2338371,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20597ee1e8f2221a7d3b740b5fd7e6d06cfb08e7","tid":2338371,"uid":43280,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202